{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-lbl","category":"Pyraminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Pyraminx","title":{"en":"Pyraminx LBL Method (Layer-by-Layer) 不再更新","zh":"金字塔层先法"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Pyraminx LBL Method (Layer-by-Layer) 不再更新</strong></p><p><strong>Move Notation</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>U</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R.</p><p><strong><br>Structure</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Center [4]</p></td><td><p>Edge [6]</p></td><td><p>Tip [4]</p></td><td><p>Corner [4]</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>Tips can be solved in any step for independence. </p><p><strong>FL Centers (First Layer)</strong></p><p>Put the non-yellow tip on the top layer, then turn the 3 yellow centers to the bottom face.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B'</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>FL Edges</strong></p><p>Insert 3 yellow edges into FL. S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>S</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U' R'\">U R U' R'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R U R'\">U' R U R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>H</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' L' U L\">U' L' U L</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U L' U' L\">U L' U' L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (R U' R')\">S (R U' R')</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>LL (Last Layer)</strong></p><p>Solve LL centers by U move, then solve 3 edges of LL using algorithms below.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>H (U' R U R')</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (U L' U' L)\">S (U L' U' L)</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑L (U R U' R') L'\">↑L (U R U' R') L'</span></p><p>H (U R U' R')</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R' (U' L' U L) R\">↑R' (U' L' U L) R</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (U' L' U L)\">S (U' L' U L)</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R' U' R U' R'\">R U' R' U' R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U L U L' U L\">L' U L U L' U L</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>金字塔层先法</strong></p><p><strong>还原尖</strong></p><p><strong>找到不含黄色的尖</strong></p><p><strong>转动记号</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>U</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R.</p><p><strong>结构</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>心 [4]</p></td><td><p>棱 [6]</p></td><td><p>尖 [4]</p></td><td><p>角 [4]</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>可在任何阶段还原尖.</p><p><strong>底心</strong></p><p>将非黄尖放在顶层，然后将三个黄心转到底面.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B'</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>底棱</strong></p><p>将三个黄棱插入底层. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>S</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U' R'\">U R U' R'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R U R'\">U' R U R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>H</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' L' U L\">U' L' U L</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U L' U' L\">U L' U' L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (R U' R')\">S (R U' R')</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R' L R\">L' R' L R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R L R' L'\">R L R' L'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2' L R L' R\">R2' L R L' R</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>顶层</strong></p><p>转U还原顶心后用下面公式还原三个顶棱.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/zh/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>H (U' R U R')</strong></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (U L' U' L)\">S (U L' U' L)</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑L (U R U' R') L'\">↑L (U R U' R') L'</span></p><p>H (U R U' R')</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R' (U' L' U L) R\">↑R' (U' L' U L) R</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"S (U' L' U L)\">S (U' L' U L)</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R' U' R U' R'\">R U' R' U' R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U L U L' U L\">L' U L U L' U L</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["U R U' R'","U' R U R'","U' L' U L","U L' U' L","S (R U' R')","S (U L' U' L)","↑L (U R U' R') L'","↑R' (U' L' U L) R","S (U' L' U L)","R U' R' U' R U' R'","L' U L U L' U L","L' R' L R","R L R' L'","R2' L R L' R"],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-lbl/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
